name: What Defines Reality?
description:
What do you believe is real?

The game is set in a dream like world where things change depending on interaction.

We plan to develop this game further after the Jam. Note that the level is a tutorial level for when we do continue development after the Jam. This is our first Game Jam so constructive criticism is encouraged. Thanks for playing

Coding, Models, and pretty much everything: Narrotor
Logo, Cover Image, Project Page: JumperGum
